# Frontend (`frontend`)

React 18 + Vite + TypeScript + TanStack Query + Tailwind + shadcn/ui. Capacitor iOS app in `ios/`.

## Commands ‚Äî run from `frontend/`
- Dev server: `npm run dev`
- Typecheck: `npx tsc -b`
- Lint: `npm run lint` (one pre-existing `src/components/ui/button.tsx` fast-refresh warning is expected ‚Äî 0 errors otherwise)
- Unit tests: `npm test` (Vitest); accessibility via `vitest-axe`
- Build: `npm run build`
- iOS sync after a build: `npx cap sync ios` (then rebuild in Xcode for native changes)

## Conventions
- API base comes from `VITE_API_BASE_URL`. Call the API via `apiFetch` (`src/api/client.ts`); admin calls via `adminFetch`. Cross-domain CSRF is handled with a token cookie + an `X-Capacitor-App` header for native traffic.
- Data fetching: TanStack Query hooks in `src/api/*` and `src/hooks/*`. Put **pure logic in `src/lib/*` and unit-test it** (the data resolvers/builders follow this pattern).
- Styling: Tailwind v4 (CSS-first) + the design tokens in `src/index.css` ‚Äî semantic tokens live in the `@theme` block and the `:root` HSL vars; there is no `tailwind.config.js`. Brand = an amber‚Üíorange gradient on a cream background. A matching Figma token file exists (see `AGENTS.md`).
- Components: child UI in `src/components/child/` and `src/pages/child/`; admin UI in `src/components/admin/`; shadcn/ui primitives in `src/components/ui/`.
- New user-facing UI needs a component test **and** a `vitest-axe` a11y check ‚Äî the app targets **WCAG 2.2 AA**.

## iOS / mobile constraints ‚Äî do NOT regress
- Form controls must stay **‚â•16px font on touch** (the `@media (pointer: coarse)` rule in `index.css`) to prevent iOS input auto-zoom. Do **not** add `maximum-scale` / `user-scalable=no` to the viewport ‚Äî that breaks WCAG 1.4.4 zoom.
- A native `AppDelegate` re-layout fixes a WKWebView cold-launch right-edge overflow; keep `viewport-fit=cover` and the safe-area (`--safe-*`) handling intact.
